      1          /***************************************************************************//**
      2           * @file
      3           * @brief This is the implementation of a very simple storage interface for either
      4           * OTA client or server.  It keeps track of only one file.  The actual storage
      5           * device is defined by the developer, but it is assumed to be a device
      6           * with a continuous block of space (such as an EEPROM).
